{"tid":1323841,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"（急）聽日 書展 三中商！","createTime":"2019-07-16T11:26:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T15:25:03.000Z","uid":227217,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"249b3154b94cfdd348d26e108e53b0a7eb934d93","tid":1323841,"uid":227217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:26:16.000Z","msg":"行動方向：勇武嘅自己諗啦，可能都係要就地取材，不過要小心啊記住！反而和理非可以做嘅比較尷尬，簡單講：<br />\n<br />\n1）每日輪流一百幾十友念經咁同想幫襯/行緊嘅人講，唔好資助中聯辦干預香港事務<br />\n<br />\n2）呢個要多啲人嘅，逼滿三中商攤位，唔俾機會同空間人買嘢<br />\n<br />\n3）喺出面天橋嗰啲派傳單<br />\n<br />\n4）痴線啲嘅，跪喺收銀附近，求大家唔好買，為下一代着想<br />\n<br />\n5）支援勇武嘅人，唔好俾佢哋被捕，幫手舌戰群儒<br />\n<br />\n總之，要多人、要度口號、要文宣、要亂！亂嘅話啲（偽）知識分子就會散水，我哋就成功"},{"pid":"b6c32347849cb7b7979b1fd460fdc9ce34f710f5","tid":1323841,"uid":227217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:28:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"65dd6c9ae577a5338a889c084691444cfefb9505","tid":1323841,"uid":227217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:28:28.000Z","msg":"唔好送錢俾中聯辦啊屌"},{"pid":"dfa1172aa2c7f0f0733722127f7f2c8a84b47e4e","tid":1323841,"uid":227217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:31:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24dbd28bda069ea1a369a5f48e5222016be1ee98","tid":1323841,"uid":227217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:32:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好益中聯辦啊"},{"pid":"b02a48f212b9897ad6cc7fff4d5c4683b8b95177","tid":1323841,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:37:23.000Z","msg":"支那書店分佈圖：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F708ZA8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx